.TP
\fB-l, --log\fR
Enable logging, output is on ~/.config/carch/carch.log
.TP
\fB-v, --version\fR
Print version information
.TP
\fB-c, --catppuccin-mocha\fR
Set theme to Catppuccin Mocha
.TP
\fB-d, --dracula\fR
Set theme to Dracula
.TP
\fB-g, --gruvbox\fR
Set theme to Gruvbox
.TP
\fB-n, --nord\fR
Set theme to Nord
.TP
\fB-r, --rose-pine\fR
